This Echo Stream client plugin provides additional logic for the Green Room use case. This use case was designed to achieve better communication experience between the VIP guests and site regular audience. Additional information about the Green Room use case can be found on the following page:

http://wiki.aboutecho.com/Use%20Case%20-%20Green%20Room

Version: 2.0 (07/18/2011)
Developed by: Echo Solutions team (Kushnir Andrew)
Documentation: http://wiki.aboutecho.com/Community-Developed-Plugins#GreenRoomReplies
